        | Our platform bridges the gap between aspiring actors, musicians, dancers, and other creative 
        | professionals with casting directors, filmmakers, and production houses. No more missed 
        | opportunities, no more scattered information—everything you need is in one place.
      
      p.lead.mb-3
        | Whether you're an aspiring actor looking for your first break, a seasoned performer seeking 
        | new roles, or a casting director searching for the perfect talent, TFI-24 brings the entire 
        | film industry ecosystem to your fingertips.
      
      h2.text-center.mb-5(style="color: #1a73e8; font-weight: 700; font-size: 2rem; margin-top: 3rem;") Why Choose TFI-24?
      
